        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">

        <div class="sidebar">
            <div class="sidebar-icons">
                <div class="logoInSidebar"> 
                    <h2><a href="/landingpage">Iskryb</a></h2>
                </div>
                <li><a class="sidebar_anchor" href='/about'>About</a></li>
                <li><a class="sidebar_anchor" href='/landingpage'>Home</a></li>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="contentcontainer">
            <div class="content">
                <div class="box item">
                    <h1>Become a
                    <span class="iskribbler">Iskribbler <span class="pen">ð“‚ƒðŸ–Š</span></span>
                    </h1>
                    <p>Write. Share. Inspire</p>
                     <ul>
                        <li><span>âœ…</span>Empowering users to express their thoughts freely.</li>
                        <li><span>âœ…</span>Building a supportive space for like-minded individuals.</li>
